        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/458/126294/458_126294_000009_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-458",
        "content": "Then said Lina: 'Fundevogel, never leave me, and I will never leave you.' Then said Fundevogel: 'Neither now, nor ever.' Said Lina: 'Be a fishpond, and I will be the duck upon it.' The cook, however, came up to them, and when she saw the pond she lay down by it, and was about to drink it up.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
